{"tid":2154260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"五等分花嫁係愛情定柯南推理類黎？","createTime":"2020-08-13T04:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T07:08:11.000Z","uid":196321,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e57743ebf80762f5b1537bdc5047e6b7dc8d34d","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"追舊番，睇完動畫覺得唔錯走去追漫畫，五姐妹成日互換，我覺得只會搞到主角不斷猜疑每一個都唔係真，平時整估主角影分身可以，但獨處時咪扮人<br />\n<br />\n仲有一花過左遊戲規則底線，有咩理由扮其他姐妹去減男主角分，減人地既分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，反而二妹明刀明槍仲好（但我最唔鍾意佢）<br />\n<br />\n仲有存在係主角記憶果個五年前女孩，其實係咪每一個小片段都係唔同女仔，只不過影相果時係老四。。。未睇哂，可以劇透我雖然我當金田一同柯南咁睇套野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，人設畫得好靚"},{"pid":"0603268024cfcc7ad86de62ba311e7b476835dd4","tid":2154260,"uid":112760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"其中一個是妹妹<br />\n謊言，隱瞞，欺騙"},{"pid":"243685de4f8061466c4a7a2f52468c15e01877f7","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0603268024cfcc7ad86de62ba311e7b476835dd4","tid":2154260,"uid":112760,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"其中一個是妹妹<br />\n謊言，隱瞞，欺騙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"人設黎講五等分係中毒男心， 巨乳又有唔同屬性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但睇到中期似鬥智多過輕鬆搞笑愛情<br />\n<br />\n我鍾意輝夜姬，之後睇左小青不能專心讀書覺得都似，之後再睇呢套卡通就似但漫畫開始唔似，變左金田一同姐係鬥智心計<br />\n<br />\n個男人應該會癲，每一刻都要猜忌對方其實係邊個/邊個扮緊"},{"pid":"697fe28a9bf8f8f19ee450ffeb323f12e5972f8c","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"仲有我形住班姐妹個樣會突然變做&ldquo;寒蟬鳴泣&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9814d812071c6d88090cb422ce4f808ae8e5db4c","tid":2154260,"uid":175208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"697fe28a9bf8f8f19ee450ffeb323f12e5972f8c","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"仲有我形住班姐妹個樣會突然變做&ldquo;寒蟬鳴泣&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"飯團藏針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3c14ab50bda8794dd6019c4ba245c9350eb44c","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9814d812071c6d88090cb422ce4f808ae8e5db4c","tid":2154260,"uid":175208,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"697fe28a9bf8f8f19ee450ffeb323f12e5972f8c","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"仲有我形住班姐妹個樣會突然變做&ldquo;寒蟬鳴泣&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"飯團藏針<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:15:18.000Z","msg":"會面容好扭曲咁講： 我地要一直維持呢份開心吧？ 風太朗君<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後懦弱既三久就好似donkidonki咁有個震撼吊頸特寫變晴天公仔<br />\n<br />\n個風格突然由溫馨轉做變態推理。。。呢期好多野都玩呢種風格 e.g.來自深淵"},{"pid":"9c41c4d09637f9dd289438214299c7fd8652d64d","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:19:36.000Z","msg":"仲有最後結局應該係風太朗以為自己同左四妹一齊，其實係家姐隊林左佢帶上老四頭帶扮元氣妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ca494e828db7f0e02ec110a25eb33a22101f11","tid":2154260,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92d6e7f76e0bc7189eb53309bbc046c1b98856aa","tid":2154260,"uid":240524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:31:04.000Z","msg":"最刺激係同人本入面一花身體有其他妹妹身體咁五合一去愛風太朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c967981b493026422dba5d5a2361a2019a99e2b","tid":2154260,"uid":196321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"s